    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <h2>Welcome to Gotorz</h2>
            <p>
                Gotorz is a leading travel platform based in the UAE, dedicated to offering seamless travel experiences for customers. Since its inception, Gotorz has been a pioneer in providing unique travel packages and easy-to-use services for individuals and businesses alike.
